        <title>Reminders from the unit for administrators</title>
        <contents>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;What can you use from this unit to support teachers?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Share the academic language analysis tool.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Direct them to the AWL and the AWL highlighter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Use the video (and others in the series) in professional development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Direct teachers to graphic organizers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Observe for implementation of these principles while observing classes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Next let's turn to a reading and reflection for supporting this emphasis on academic language development in your program.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
